<section style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-top: -3px; margin-right: -3px; float: right; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);"></section><section class="" style="height: 3em; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section class="" style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-left: -3px; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);"></section><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 10px; margin-top: -3em; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><br  /></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">“你长大之后想干什么呢？”</span></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">“你的理想是什么？”</span></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">“到了大学你想读什么专业呢？”</span></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">…...</span></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">“我想学化学，但我还想当律师。”</span></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px;">“孩子，这不现实。”</span><br  /></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="line-height: 1.6;"><br  /></span></p></section></section></section></section><section class="" style="margin-top: -2.9em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-right: -3px; float: right; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);"></section><section style="height: 3em; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-top: -3px; margin-left: -3px; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);"></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">也许在成长的过程中，我们不断地被别人问到自己的理想，但大家被问到时能够立刻就给出准确的答案吗？还是会因为自己的爱好实在是太多了，难以从中选择而感到焦虑呢？但人生真的只能是一条单行线吗？今天小编就给大家推荐一场有关兴趣发展与职业选择的 TED，看看Emilie Wapnic是怎么做到“不专一”的。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">主讲人既是一位作家，也是一位艺术家，她有广泛的爱好，并且从事过各种职业。她不能接受必须从自己的兴趣中选择其一作为终生职业而舍弃其它这件事，但她也怀疑过自己这样朝秦暮楚的行为是不是不对的。最终，她的答案是否定的。她把像她一样对待爱好和职业的人称作“多重潜力者（Multipotentialite）”，你是否属于这种类型呢？</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>--Why some of us don't have one true calling?</strong></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>--为什么有些人不能听从自己内心真实的呼唤？</strong></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br  /></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="height: 2.6em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style=" transform: rotate(-45deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(-45deg); -moz-transform: rotate(-45deg); -o-transform: rotate(-45deg); margin-top: -1em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 2em; height: 2em; margin: auto; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="height: 100%; border-left-width: 0.2em; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); border-bottom-width: 0.2em; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent !important;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-left: -3px; margin-right: -3px; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);"></section><section class="" style="border-bottom-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); border-left-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 10px; width: 100%; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">首先Emilie分享了她自己的经历。她无法长期一头钻进某一个单一领域中，而总是做所谓的“浅尝辄止”。她认为一件事情做到已经很有成就感时，再往下进行，厌倦心理便会驱使她放下并去尝试新的事物。她追求的多元化正是满足了她广泛兴趣爱好的需求，这也给她带来无限的成就感。</span></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">小时候我们经常被问到长大想要干什么，大人们具体关心的其实并不是你的梦想，只是希望得到孩子们可爱的回应而已。而到了高中，“你将来想要干什么？”似乎就变成了让我们寝食难安的问题。Emilie认为我们的文化一直在向我们灌输着一个理念——在自己的兴趣中作出选择和舍弃。但是在一生中心无旁骛地做一件事情是不是被过分理想化了呢？我们真的能够找到它并为之奋斗终生吗？</span></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">因此她提出了“多重潜力者（Multipotentialite）”这个概念，即一种具有多种兴趣并不断追求创新的人，一种愿意尝试多种职业的人，一种所谓“不专一”的人。</span></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lZxqO3dCoYgHJaoRzf7PBKxdKv0MOIGAS1IJ0btPG835AdGG1hP9cfqLC7EsyPx86FueV0OZicY4RvicxdzjYcdQ/0?wx_fmt=png" class="" data-type="png" data-ratio="0.5625" data-w="640"  /></section></section></section><section class="" style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; margin-top: -3px; margin-right: -3px; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);"></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br  /></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">她举出了许多人的例子来说明多重潜力者的大量存在，有作为弦乐器工匠的心理医生，有作为插画作家、杂志编辑、创意总监、教师的企业家……</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">她认为多重潜力者有三大超能力：</span></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lZxqO3dCoYgHJaoRzf7PBKxdKv0MOIGAetiakfuwpP1Y2TpFQNVfMv36vDolibTeUbZklXDgHzpFED94Wv7XE61w/0?wx_fmt=png" class="" data-type="png" data-ratio="0.5625" data-w="640"  /></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">其一，多重潜力者往往具有丰富知识，往往能结合两个或两个以上的领域，从各领域的交叉处寻求创新，而创新点往往就出现在那些结合处。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">其二，多重潜力者善于观察和实践，学习能力超强。他们经常成为各个领域的初学者，去学习新领域的知识。但这并非完全是从零开始，而是不经意间就把之前的旧知识运用到新事物上。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">其三，多重潜力者勇于尝试新事物，在适应能力方面自然能够超越常人，灵活应对各种事物。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; margin-bottom: -0.65em; margin-top: 0.95em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); width: 99.9%; float: left; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-top: -3px; border-radius: 100%; float: right; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);"></section></section><section class="" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: -1em; vertical-align: top; padding: 3px 10px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br  /></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">其实，Emilie并不是鼓励大家都去成为一名多重潜力者。有许多“专家型”的人，他们愿意去钻研一件事物，愿意为之倾注毕生精力。所以她鼓励的是让我们接受自己内心的想法，be ourselves!她呼吁，如果你是一名多重潜力者，或者看完这场TED才知道自己原来属于其中一员，那么就去尝试接受不同的知识，永远保持一颗好奇心，去探索各个领域，让自我引领我们前进吧！</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br  /></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">在现实生活中，也许我们会被自己的专业所限，而向发展其它兴趣做出一些妥协。但其实我们又拥有着大量机会让我们去接受新事物，去发展自己的各类兴趣。我们可以去旁听别的学院的专业课，可以上慕课学一门从未接触过的领域的课程，可以辅修甚至修一门双学位。我们可以手撕数理化的同时而又保持一份文艺，学几种乐器，做一次艺术创作等等。Follow your heart,人生可以不是一条单行线！</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">戳一下阅读原文可以观看完整TED哦~</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: right;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px;">晓玲 | 审核</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: right;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px;">子明 | 编辑</span></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="display: inline-block; padding: 5px; margin-left: 2.5em; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp; &nbsp;关注我们，做你自己</p></section><section class="" style="text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 99.9%; float: left; height: 0px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-top: -3px; float: right; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);"></section></section><section class="" style="width: 3em; height: 3em; margin-top: -1.5em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lZxqO3dCoYgHJaoRzf7PBKxdKv0MOIGAHLpRWkCHMReXu8J8icGYgbBO5tR4Qib5PTtNVsDArWlkBLgPNJS9BOBA/0?wx_fmt=gif); background-size: cover; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat;" class=""><section class="" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img style="width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/lZxqO3dCoYgHJaoRzf7PBKxdKv0MOIGAHLpRWkCHMReXu8J8icGYgbBO5tR4Qib5PTtNVsDArWlkBLgPNJS9BOBA/0?wx_fmt=gif" class="" data-type="gif" data-ratio="1" data-w="72"  /></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><img data-type="gif" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/lZxqO3dCoYgHAZ5mVzHOticSbFexnUf9AL0paWibiaMkd10F3iaDBtfIHErlf1a9SJ7WHsusgK2ZZo2Vg2RorFsHCA/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.5555555555555556" data-w="900"  /><br  /></p>